Aryselmalyr
Fhaoralusyolkiir (. It would continue to stand following Aryselmalyn Empires demise not becoming entirely abandoned and left to ruin until . As the years passed, much of the city built into the cliffside would be buried by collapsing caverns.
In the , the Church of Deep Sashelas took up residence in the palace once lived in by the garrison citys commanders, turning it into a temple to their god. This state of affairs would continue well into the 14 century DR, with the city still retaining some vestiges of its grandeur.
